    • Method Detail

      • getTimeTable

        public static void getTimeTable(java.util.List<SubscriptionItem> subscriptions,
                AsyncHttpResponseHandler callback)
        Get the time-table for the passed subscriptions. The timetable covers the weeks containing YESTERDAY and TODAY. If this method is called on a Monday, last week and this entire week is returned from TimeEdit. The callback will receive the entire TimeEdit HTML on success.
        Parameters:
        subscriptions - List of subscriptions (rooms, courses, classes)
        callback - The callback that will receive the TimeEdit HTML.

      • search

        public static void search(java.lang.String term,
          AsyncHttpResponseHandler handler)
        Search TimeEdit for raw text. The callback will receive the entire TimeEdit HTML on success.
        Parameters:
        term - Raw text to search TimeEdit for.
        handler - The callback that will receive TimeEdit HTML.
